====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# [[mugwort]], especially [[Chinese mugwort]] {{gloss|{{taxlink|Artemisia argyi|species}}}}, whose [[leaves]] are used to make [[moxa]]
#* {{zh-x|彼 采 艾 兮。一日 不見、如 三-歲 兮。|There that one is gathering the '''mugwort'''! A day without seeing that one, is like three years!|ref=Shijing}}
# {{lb|zh|obsolete}} [[green]]
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[pale]]; [[greyish]] [[white]]
#* {{zh-x|五十 曰 艾，服 官-政。|When he is fifty, we say, 'He is getting '''grey''';' he can discharge all the duties of an officer.|ref=Liji}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[elderly]] person
#* {{zh-x|^凡 童-少 鑒 淺 而 志 盛，長-艾 識 堅 而 氣 衰。|Ordinarily, the youths are shallow-minded yet strong-willed; the '''elderly''' are firm in wisdom and dwindling in spirit.|ref='''6th century''' Liu Xie 劉勰, 《文心雕龍》''The Mind of Literature and Carved Dragons''}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[end]]; to [[stop]]
#: {{zh-x|方興{xīnɡ}未艾|to be in the ascendant}}
#* {{zh-x|夜 如何 其{jī}、夜 未 艾。|How goes the night? The night has not yet '''ended'''.|ref=Shijing}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[beautiful]] [[lady]]
#* {{zh-x|知 好色，則 慕 少-艾；|When he becomes conscious of the attractions of beauty, his desire is towards young and '''beautiful women'''.|ref=Mengzi}}
# {{lb|zh|obsolete}} to [[nurture]]; to [[foster]]
#* {{zh-x|樂 只 君子、保-艾 爾 後。|To be rejoiced in are ye, gentlemen; May ye preserve and '''maintain''' your posterity!|ref=Shijing}}
#* {{zh-x|君子 萬年、福祿 艾 之。|May our sovereign live for ten thousand years, '''sustained''' in his happiness and wealth!|ref=Shijing}}
# {{lb|zh|historical}} an ancient place in modern-day {{w|Xiushui County}}, [[Jiangxi]]
# {{lb|zh|historical}} a mountain in modern-day {{w|Xintai}}, [[Shandong]]
# {{zh-used2|t}}
# {{surname|zh}}

